<!DOCTYPE html><html xmlns:cc="http://creativecommons.org/ns#"><head prefix="og: http://ogp.me/ns# fb: http://ogp.me/ns/fb# medium-com: http://ogp.me/ns/fb/medium-com#"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"><title>JSX Looks Like An Abomination — JavaScript Scene — Medium</title><link rel="canonical" href="https://medium.com/javascript-scene/jsx-looks-like-an-abomination-1c1ec351a918"><meta name="title" content="JSX Looks Like An Abomination — JavaScript Scene"><meta name="referrer" content="always"><meta name="description" content="But it’s Good for You"><meta property="og:site_name" content="Medium"><meta property="og:title" content="JSX Looks Like An Abomination — JavaScript Scene"><meta property="og:url" content="https://medium.com/javascript-scene/jsx-looks-like-an-abomination-1c1ec351a918"><meta property="og:image" content="https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*x9qGjkuqS9wQOkyXBk7fHA.jpeg"><meta property="fb:app_id" content="542599432471018"><meta property="og:description" content="But it’s Good for You"><meta name="twitter:site" content="@Medium"><meta name="twitter:image:src" content="https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*x9qGjkuqS9wQOkyXBk7fHA.jpeg"><link rel="publisher" href="https://plus.google.com/103654360130207659246"><link rel="author" href="https://medium.com/@_ericelliott"><meta name="author" content="Eric Elliott"><meta property="og:type" content="article"><meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image"><meta property="article:publisher" content="https://www.facebook.com/medium"><meta property="article:author" content="https://medium.com/@_ericelliott"><meta property="fb:smart_publish:robots" content="noauto"><meta property="article:published_time" content="2015-05-20T07:18:16.763Z"><meta name="twitter:creator" content="@_ericelliott"><meta name="twitter:app:name:iphone" content="Medium"><meta name="twitter:app:id:iphone" content="8282562